You took me from being an independent manager working out of my house, to a leading 40 under 40, Power Player, respected executive. Hallwood Media will always hold a very special place in my heart. My team, clients and I look to the New Year with great excitement and hunger! We have some big announcements coming soon, and new worlds and opportunities to explore. 2023 is about to be the best yet.

Happy Birthday to my Brother, my ace and my fellow 2022 Billboard R&B and Hip Hop Power Player Brennen Bryant @iamladell. So proud of you and your growth over the last almost 5 years you’ve been working with me. Your commitment, hard work, and most importantly loyalty is always so appreciated and inspiring to not just me but all your peers. I love you and got you for life. We just getting started. Enjoy your day. You deserve it all!!! Shout out @briatheboss aka PR Queen 👑.

Happy Birthday to my brother, my partner, my best man, my best friend, and Noah’s Godfather. Crazy reminiscing last night how far we’ve come, and how far we plan to take it still. You gave my life a new purpose and new path almost 9 years ago taking me on this journey with you. And for that I am forever grateful. Tonight we make another movie. But our lives together have been a movie! And the best is yet to come. I’m rockin with you till the wheels fall off. Love you my brother Shane. The world is yours!

Happy Valentine’s Day to my beautiful bride @livworldwide ❤️ This day was so magical and so is every day I get to be your husband. Together we made Noah and our amazing family and home. This is the exact life I dreamed of and we just getting started! Through ups and downs you are always there for me and I will always be there for you. Each day gets better. So grateful I get to spend the rest of my life with you. I love you Ashley ❤️
Such an incredible 2 Michelin star Omakase experience last night with my Valentine @LivWorldwide at our new favorite sushi spot @Asanebo_Restaurant 🍣💘

Can’t believe my baby is 2 years old today!!! Time flies when you have a perfect baby and the best partner and mother I could have ever hoped for. Noah and I are so lucky to have you Mommy @LivWorldWide. I think it’s time we make anotha one lol. But for now we celebrate the life of Noah. Our biggest blessing and greatest joy. Being your Dad is the best and most fulfilling Job I’ve ever had. Now let’s party! Born TWO be wild 🙈 🎉 🎂

Happy Birthday to the living legend @SteveRifkind. Proud to call you a brother and a friend. Appreciate all the guidance and support and stories and lessons you share with me. You have become one of the most genuine people in my life. Excited for what we got cooking up. The best is yet to come. More life!

Better late than never but sending a big happy Belated Birthday to my real brother, my parents other son (favorite?), HLP and MC of my wedding @TorontoCharlie. Over 15 years of friendship still going strong. Been around the world together. Can’t wait for more laughs and more adventures. Miss you always. Just move to LA already. Love you dog. More life! P.s. had to post the most awkward dolphin pic of all time lmao 🤣 🐬 🎉

Born Two Be Wild 🐒🎉 Noah’s Second Birthday Party was so much fun. Friends, family, tacos, exotic animals, dinosaurs, a ball pit and a jumping castle! Thanks for all who came out. So few made it in the photos but the memories are there. Thanks for all the love and support from all of our loved ones over the past 2 years. It really takes a village and @livworldwide and I are so grateful. Noah, the world is yours my son!
Our little cub Noah in his Purim costume for school today 🥹🥰🐻 Hope this makes you all smile😊

Happy Birthday to my brother Cheese @JjasonG 🥳 Already a Legend and we just getting started. Love you bro. Spending your birthday recording the 🐐 and I know it’s exactly where you want to be. Thanks for the inspiration, love and loyalty. Now watch what we do next. Belated celebrations when you get back!

Happy Birthday to the love of my life, my wife @LivWorldWide. So grateful for you and to God that I found you and that we get to spend the rest of our lives together. Cheers to 33, more trips, more kids, and more memories. Love you babe. For now and forever❤️

Congrats to my brother @kyjoshuaa  on being recognized in this month’s @HitsDD. Proud of you and your growth. Been working together for over a decade. Grateful to have you back out in LA with me building this empire. @2wenty_2wenty 📈📈

Couple dope new pieces for the crib  from my brother @BournRich. Love the Muhammad Ali joint already on the wall in my home office. Ali’s been such an inspiration to me my whole life and been looking for the right piece. Him and my great Aunt ran a Parkinson’s foundation together and I had a personalized autographed photo from him but his writing faded 🤦‍♂️. Now I get to be inspired from the legend and the creativity from the art while I work. Bourn also gifted us this incredible Tom & Jerry silk screen painting for my son Noah and he LOVES it! Check out his work at www.BournRich.com 🖼️ 🎨

Had the pleasure to help organize an incredible Freedom Seder this past weekend with the @BJEAlliance @AutoReverse and Rabbi @MichelleMissaghieh. Such a special night. First of many. Very proud and excited to be able to provide a platform for entertainment industry professionals from the Black and Jewish communities to discuss unity, freedom and how we can come together as one. Look out for more great events coming this year. And Happy Passover to all celebrating tonight and observing throughout the week.

3 generations of LitWinning! Happy Fathers Day to my amazing Dad and Happy Father’s Day to me. Becoming a Dad myself made me truly appreciate you even more Dad, and how important your role was and still is today in my life. Your the first person I speak to every morning (or last before bed depending how late I stay up). My best friend and greatest role model. Becoming a father myself has been the biggest  blessing and most fulfilling role I’ve ever had in life. Noah has given my life real purpose. Motivates me to become the best version of myself and best man I can be to set an example and provide for my son. Each day gets better. Love you Dad & Love you Noah. Happy Father’s Day to all the real Dad’s out there ❤️

Happy Aniversary babe. Been legally married over 2.5 years but today marks one year since our epic celebration and getting married before God and all our loved ones. Love you so much Ashley. Marriage has its challenges of course, like life, but we overcome them together as partners and our love and bond just keeps growing stronger! I Love you @livworldwide today and forever ❤️

Image sent from my Dad. As a Dad now myself there is nothing I would love more than to see peace in the world. Peace in Israel. Coexistence. A 2 state solution. Human compassion. Recognition that all human life is precious regardless of what country they are born in or religion they are born into. Condemnation and no justification for the slaughter of innocent woman, children and eslderly. Today this seems like a dream but let us hope and pray. I pray for the people of Israel. I pray for the people of Palestine. I pray that the terrorists who seek death and destruction of any Jew or Israeli (whether Jewish or not) and have no regard for their own people or any human life are eliminated so that peace and coexistence is possible. Praying for a better and safer future 🙏🏽🙏🏽🙏🏽

Day One In Johannesburg & Soweto. First day in South Africa! 🇿🇦 Just 4 hours of exploring and already a life changing experience. Grateful the work I do brings me to these amazing places. And beyond grateful for how privileged and blessed I am and never take it for granted. Such a beautiful country and people. Went to the Apartheid museum, a squatters camp in Soweto, Nelson Mandela’s house, the monument for the 600 children shot in 197 and met the inspiring Antoinette, the woman in the second last slide, and little girl in last slide. Very sad and moving experience. But the history here also gives so much hope! Thank you @AutumnRowe for taking me on this unforgettable journey with you.

On this morning’s 5am safari drive at the Madikwe Game Reserve in South Africa on the border Of Botswana I had the special privilege of witnessing a pack of Cheetahs hunt and catch an Impala. After the mother made her kill, the 3 cubs then ate their meal while the she sat on high alert watching out for the lion lurking close by. Such a rare and lucky sighting. Tons of photos and videos coming soon just wanted to share this special one first. Been here less than 24 hours and already one of the most incredible experiences of my life. Nature is magnificent! Africa is beautiful! Being among these animals in their natural habitat is magical. So much beauty in the world. Can’t wait to discover and appreciate more of it! 🐆🐆🐆🇿🇦🇿🇦🇿🇦🌍🌍🌍🙏🏽

My first African Safari. I say first because I intend to come back the rest of my life with my family. Such an incredible experience. Definitely one of the best of my life that I have been dreaming about since I was a child. Pictures from my iPhone can never do it justice.
